<p begin='00:00:18.552' end='00:00:19.987' tts:textAlign='left'  space='preserve'><span style='block'>GENTLEMEN!</span></p>
<p begin='00:00:20.020' end='00:00:22.689' tts:textAlign='left'  space='preserve'><span style='block'>( CHEERS AND APPLAUSE )<br/>&gt;&gt; THANK YOU. THANK YOU.</span></p>
<p begin='00:00:22.723' end='00:00:25.392' tts:textAlign='left'  space='preserve'><span style='block'>&gt;&gt; John: MY FIRST QUESTION IS<br/>ACTUALLY MAZIAR, FOR YOU.</span></p>
