<p begin='00:00:29.062' end='00:00:30.397' tts:textAlign='left'  space='preserve'><span style='block'>&gt;&gt; John: THE REAL ONE. THAT&apos;S<br/>RIGHT.</span></p>
<p begin='00:00:30.430' end='00:00:33.066' tts:textAlign='left'  space='preserve'><span style='block'>&gt;&gt; OH OKAY.<br/>&gt;&gt; John: THE ONE THAT IS</span></p>
<p begin='00:00:33.100' end='00:00:37.137' tts:textAlign='left'  space='preserve'><span style='block'>SLIGHTLY LESS COMPELLING TO LOOK<br/>AT.</span></p>
<p begin='00:00:37.171' end='00:00:38.038' tts:textAlign='left'  space='preserve'><span style='block'>&gt;&gt; WELL THANK YOU.<br/>&gt;&gt; John: WITH THAT IN MIND,</span></p>
<p begin='00:00:38.071' end='00:00:39.406' tts:textAlign='left'  space='preserve'><span style='block'>WITH THAT IN MIND, WHEN YOU<br/>FIRST HEARD--</span></p>
<p begin='00:00:39.439' end='00:00:41.542' tts:textAlign='left'  space='preserve'><span style='block'>&gt;&gt; YOU&apos;RE ONE TO TALK.<br/>&gt;&gt; John: WHEN YOU FIRST HEARD</span></p>
<p begin='00:00:41.575' end='00:00:46.113' tts:textAlign='left'  space='preserve'><span style='block'>THAT GAEL WAS GOING TO PLAY<br/>YOU IN A MOVIE, AND YOU</span></p>
<p begin='00:00:46.146' end='00:00:49.349' tts:textAlign='left'  space='preserve'><span style='block'>LOOKED AT A PHOTO OF HIM DID YOU<br/>THINK ( BLEEP ) YEAH?</span></p>
