<p begin='00:00:54.621' end='00:00:55.956' tts:textAlign='left'  space='preserve'><span style='block'>&gt;&gt; THAT&apos;S TRUE. THAT&apos;S<br/>EXACLY, THAT&apos;S EXACTLY TRUE.</span></p>
<p begin='00:00:55.989' end='00:00:59.359' tts:textAlign='left'  space='preserve'><span style='block'>I MEAN, GAEL HAS BEEN ONE OF MY<br/>FAVORITE ACTORS SINCE HE WAS IN</span></p>
<p begin='00:00:59.393' end='00:01:03.430' tts:textAlign='left'  space='preserve'><span style='block'>&quot;Y TU MAMA TAMBIEN&quot; AND &quot;AMORES<br/>PERROS&quot;</span></p>
