<p begin='00:01:05.465' end='00:01:09.636' tts:textAlign='left'  space='preserve'><span style='block'>( CHEERS AND APPLAUSE ).</span></p>
<p begin='00:01:09.670' end='00:01:17.878' tts:textAlign='left'  space='preserve'><span style='block'>THE GOOD THING ABOUT GAEL IS<br/>THAT HE IS NOT A STEREOTYPEICAL</span></p>
