<p begin='00:01:32.426' end='00:01:35.395' tts:textAlign='left'  space='preserve'><span style='block'>&gt;&gt; John: SO, ON YOUR END GAEL,<br/>YOU&apos;RE IN A TRICKY SPOT, BECAUSE</span></p>
<p begin='00:01:35.429' end='00:01:39.633' tts:textAlign='left'  space='preserve'><span style='block'>IT MUST HAVE BEEN STRANGE TO BE<br/>DOING THOSE PRISON SCENES</span></p>
