<p begin='00:01:47.741' end='00:01:48.909' tts:textAlign='left'  space='preserve'><span style='block'>TO HAVE ON IN YOUR HEAD.</span></p>
<p begin='00:01:48.942' end='00:01:50.043' tts:textAlign='left'  space='preserve'><span style='block'>&gt;&gt; IT IS, IT IS.</span></p>
<p begin='00:01:50.077' end='00:01:53.280' tts:textAlign='left'  space='preserve'><span style='block'>AND, ALSO, THERE WAS ANOTHER<br/>ADDED PRESSURE, THAT WE WERE</span></p>
<p begin='00:01:53.313' end='00:01:56.517' tts:textAlign='left'  space='preserve'><span style='block'>SHOOTING IN A REAL PRISON<br/>SOMETIMES WITH PEOPLE IN</span></p>
<p begin='00:01:56.550' end='00:02:00.888' tts:textAlign='left'  space='preserve'><span style='block'>SOLITARY CONFINEMENT RIGHT<br/>THERE, AND RIGHT BESIDE THE CELL</span></p>
<p begin='00:02:00.921' end='00:02:03.857' tts:textAlign='left'  space='preserve'><span style='block'>THAT WE WERE, THERE WERE PEOPLE<br/>THAT WERE THERE FOR, I DON&apos;T</span></p>
<p begin='00:02:03.891' end='00:02:10.931' tts:textAlign='left'  space='preserve'><span style='block'>KNOW HOW MANY WEEKS, FOR RAPE<br/>AND WE WERE DOING THIS ACT, AND</span></p>
<p begin='00:02:10.964' end='00:02:11.565' tts:textAlign='left'  space='preserve'><span style='block'>YOU KNOW, SOMETIMES, YES.</span></p>
<p begin='00:02:11.598' end='00:02:12.766' tts:textAlign='left'  space='preserve'><span style='block'>THAT&apos;S A PROBLEM WITH FILM.</span></p>
<p begin='00:02:12.799' end='00:02:16.403' tts:textAlign='left'  space='preserve'><span style='block'>SOMETIMES YOU FALL INTO THIS<br/>KIND OF POINT WHERE YOU THINK</span></p>
<p begin='00:02:16.436' end='00:02:22.409' tts:textAlign='left'  space='preserve'><span style='block'>THIS REENACTMENT, THIS<br/>REINTERPRETATION, IS IT THIS</span></p>
<p begin='00:02:22.442' end='00:02:23.610' tts:textAlign='left'  space='preserve'><span style='block'>WORTH IT?</span></p>
<p begin='00:02:23.644' end='00:02:26.046' tts:textAlign='left'  space='preserve'><span style='block'>ARE WE GOING TO DO SOMETHING<br/>THAT IS GOING TO CONNECT, THAT&apos;S</span></p>
