<p begin='00:02:32.286' end='00:02:34.087' tts:textAlign='left'  space='preserve'><span style='block'>MAZIAR&apos;S COMPELLING STORY AND<br/>HIS INTERPRETATION OF WHAT HE</span></p>
<p begin='00:02:34.121' end='00:02:38.892' tts:textAlign='left'  space='preserve'><span style='block'>WENT THROUGH, WE ALL THE TIME<br/>KEPT THE BOATS FLOATING AND FELT</span></p>
