<p begin='00:02:53.407' end='00:02:55.709' tts:textAlign='left'  space='preserve'><span style='block'>&gt;&gt; WELL IT&apos;S THE CONTINUATION OF<br/>SOMETHING THAT WAS STARTED IN</span></p>
