<p begin='00:03:15.295' end='00:03:17.097' tts:textAlign='left'  space='preserve'><span style='block'>THOUSANDS OF PEOPLE WHO ARE<br/>GOING THROUGH THE SAME THING--</span></p>
<p begin='00:03:17.130' end='00:03:21.869' tts:textAlign='left'  space='preserve'><span style='block'>NOT ONLY IN IRAN, BUT ALSO IN<br/>OTHER COUNTRIES.</span></p>
