<p begin='00:04:12.352' end='00:04:17.324' tts:textAlign='left'  space='preserve'><span style='block'>THE FACT THAT MAZIAR CAME OUT,<br/>REALIZING THAT SOLITARY</span></p>
<p begin='00:04:17.357' end='00:04:21.962' tts:textAlign='left'  space='preserve'><span style='block'>CONFINEMENT IS TORTURE AND IT IS<br/>AN ACCEPTED-- AN ACCEPTED</span></p>
<p begin='00:04:21.995' end='00:04:24.531' tts:textAlign='left'  space='preserve'><span style='block'>PRACTICE ALL OVER THE WORLD.<br/>&gt;&gt; John: RIGHT. RIGHT.</span></p>
<p begin='00:04:24.565' end='00:04:27.901' tts:textAlign='left'  space='preserve'><span style='block'>&gt;&gt; AND ANOTHER ADDED ELEMENT<br/>THAT UNITED US IS THE FACT THAT</span></p>
