<p begin='00:04:40.747' end='00:04:42.783' tts:textAlign='left'  space='preserve'><span style='block'>I FEEL LIKE, WHAT, THEY SUSTAIN<br/>THE HAIR GEL INDUSTRY?</span></p>
<p begin='00:04:42.816' end='00:04:46.286' tts:textAlign='left'  space='preserve'><span style='block'>&gt;&gt; YES, THE HAIR GEL, HAIR GEL<br/>WOULD BE EXTINCT IF IT WERE NOT</span></p>
